      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节团圆瓜子专题页</title>\n<style>\n    :root {\n        --color-primary: #C62828;\n        --color-secondary: #FFD54F;\n        --color-bg: #F4F4F5;\n        --color-accent: #8D6E63;\n        --color-light: #FFF8E1;\n    }\n    body {\n        font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif;\n        margin: 0;\n        background-color: var(--color-bg);\n        color: var(--color-accent);\n        line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    header, section, footer {\n        padding: 2rem;\n        max-width: 1200px;\n        margin: auto;\n    }\n    h1, h2 {\n        color: var(--color-primary);\n    }\n    p {\n        color: var(--color-accent);\n    }\n    #hero-banner {\n        background-color: var(--color-secondary);\n        text-align: center;\n        padding: 4rem 2rem;\n    }\n    #hero-banner h1 {\n        font-size: 2.5rem;\n        margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n    #product-highlights {\n        background-color: var(--color-light);\n    }\n    #festival-story {\n        background-color: var(--color-bg);\n    }\n    #interactive-countdown {\n        background-color: var(--color-secondary);\n        color: var(--color-primary);\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    #purchase-section {\n        background-color: var(--color-light);\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    #purchase-section button {\n        background-color: var(--color-primary);\n        color: #fff;\n        border: none;\n        padding: 0.8rem 2rem;\n        font-size: 1rem;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    #purchase-section button:hover {\n        background-color: #b71c1c;\n    }\n    #reviews-and-shares {\n        background-color: var(--color-bg);\n    }\n    footer {\n        background-color: var(--color-primary);\n        color: #fff;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<section id=\"hero-banner\">\n    <h1>春节团圆，好嗑新疆葵花籽</h1>\n    <p>浓浓年味，香脆可口，来自新疆的优质葵花籽，为团圆添味。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"product-highlights\">\n    <h2>源自新疆，品质精选</h2>\n    <p>小包装更方便，价格亲民，香气浓郁，每一口都是自然的馈赠。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"festival-story\">\n    <h2>嗑瓜子的春节故事</h2>\n    <p>一家人围坐，笑声与瓜子脆响交织，成就最温暖的节日记忆。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"interactive-countdown\">\n    <h2>春节倒计时</h2>\n    <p>距离春节还有 <strong id=\"countdown\">10 天</strong>，快来一起迎接团圆时刻吧！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"purchase-section\">\n    <h2>立即购买</h2>\n    <p>优惠价仅 29.9 元，全国包邮，马上点击购买，提前备齐年货。</p>\n    <button>立即购买</button>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"reviews-and-shares\">\n    <h2>用户评价与分享</h2>\n    <p>精选真实好评，分享你的春节嗑瓜子故事，让更多人感受节日温情。</p>\n</section>\n\n<footer id=\"footer-info\">\n    <h2>品牌介绍</h2>\n    <p>新疆葵花籽品牌，致力于高品质农产品供应。联系电话：400-123-4567 | 促销信息请关注官方微信。© 2024 品牌版权所有。</p>\n</footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
